---
layout: layout.njk
title: Interview Guides for Tech Roles
metaTitle: "Tech Interview Guides | Askia Blog"
metaDescription: "Structured interview guides across software, infrastructure, data, product, design, revenue, finance, operations, and leadership roles, published as a dedicated interview sublibrary inside the blog."
breadcrumbs:
  - name: "Home"
    url: "/"
  - name: "Resources"
    url: "/resources/"
  - name: "Career Intelligence"
    url: "/blog/"
  - name: "Interview Guides"
    url: "/blog/interview/"
---
<div class="resource-theme-page">
<section class="blog-hero resource-theme-hero">
  <div class="container blog-hero-grid">
    <div class="blog-hero-copy">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Interview Intelligence</p>
      <h1 class="blog-hero-title">Interview Guides Inside the Blog</h1>
      <p class="blog-hero-subtitle">Role-based and topic-based interview guides covering many more job types across tech, product, data, design, revenue, finance, operations, and leadership.</p>
      <div class="blog-hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/interview-prep/">Get Interview Prep Help</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/blog/salary/">Browse Salary Guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-hero-media">
      <div class="blog-hero-image">
        <img src="/assets/blog/interview-calibration.jpg" alt="Interview preparation visuals." loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
        <span class="holo-badge">INTERVIEW READY</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set interviewCategoryGroups = blogInterviewPages | groupby("categories[0]") %}
{% set interviewRoleGroups = blogInterviewPages | groupby("role") %}

<section class="section section-tight">
  <div class="container two-col-grid">
    <div class="content-panel">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Quick answer</h2>
      <p>This library is designed to help candidates prepare better answers, not memorize generic scripts. Use the guides to sharpen your examples, tradeoff explanations, and seniority signal before interviews start.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-panel">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">How to use these guides</h2>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Start with the role or topic closest to your target loop.</li>
        <li>Prepare three to five reusable stories before you memorize more questions.</li>
        <li>Use the guide to improve structure, not to sound rehearsed.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-tight">
  <div class="container two-col-grid">
    <div class="content-panel">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Browse by role</h2>
      <ul class="checklist">
        {% for group in interviewRoleGroups %}
        <li>{{ group[0] }}: {{ group[1] | length }} guide{% if group[1] | length != 1 %}s{% endif %}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="content-panel">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Browse by role family</h2>
      <ul class="checklist">
        {% for group in interviewCategoryGroups %}
        <li>{{ group[0] }}: {{ group[1] | length }} guide{% if group[1] | length != 1 %}s{% endif %}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section blog-grid-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="blog-grid">
      {% for post in blogInterviewPages | reverse %}
      <article class="blog-card">
        <a class="blog-card-image" href="/blog/interview/{{ post.slug }}/">
          <img src="{{ post.featuredImage }}" alt="{{ post.imageAlt }}" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <div class="blog-card-body">
          <div class="blog-card-meta">
            {% for category in post.categories %}
              <span class="category-pill">{{ category }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          <h2><a href="/blog/interview/{{ post.slug }}/">{{ post.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.description }}</p>
          <div class="blog-card-foot">
            <span>{{ post.readTime }}</span>
            <span>{{ post.publishDate }}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set featuredMarketsTitle = "Markets where interview signal matters most" %}
{% set featuredMarketsSubtitle = "These city pages add local hiring context to the interview library and create stronger paths into coaching offers." %}
{% include "featured-markets.njk" %}

</div>

<script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "CollectionPage",
    "name": "Askia Interview Guides",
    "description": "Structured interview guides across technical, product, design, revenue, finance, operations, and leadership roles covering question patterns, stronger answers, and prep strategy.",
    "url": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}"
  }
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "name": "Interview guide pages",
    "itemListElement": [
      {% for post in blogInterviewPages | reverse %}
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": {{ loop.index }},
        "name": "{{ post.title }}",
        "url": "{{ site.url }}/blog/interview/{{ post.slug }}/"
      }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    ]
  }
</script>
